	addLang('moon.event.p.0'  , "West, behind the glass, you see a scary-looking machine with glowing green tubes that are connected to Princess Selena held inside a yellow cocoon. On a wall near you stands a panel that reads <br />'Selena, power draining is IN PROGRESS. DO NOT APPROACH! IN CASE OF EMERGENCY ONLY - BREAK GLASS. <br />Note, this will terminate the specimen if done while draining is in process.'");
	addLang('moon.event.p.1'  , "West, you see a scary-looking machine with green tubes that are connected to Princess Selena held inside a yellow cocoon. On a wall near you stands a panel that reads <br />'Selena, power draining is ON HOLD.'");

	addLang('moon.event.q.0'  , "As you approach the machine, an emergency shutdown program breaks the tubes from the cocoon, it falls on the ground and breaks, gravely injuring the weakened Princess. You rush towards the dying Princess, but there is nothing you can do. With her dying breath, Selena transfers what remains of her power to you and you hear a quiet 'Thank you' in your head.");
	addLang('moon.event.q.1'  , "The body of Princess Selena lies here, breathless, but still majestic.");
	addLang('moon.event.q.2'  , "You gently remove the tubes, free Princess Selena from the cocoon and put her on the floor. She is alive, but as long as Queen Menace is not defeated, she is not safe.");
	addLang('moon.event.q.3'  , "Princess Selena lies here, unconscious, but alive");

	addLang('moon.event.r.0'  , "You see a gigantic black changeling enchantress standing before you, connected to a strange machine with glowing green tubes. She looks ecstatic and powerful. She is now limited in movement, but still extremely dangerous at close range.");
	addLang('moon.event.r.1'  , "You see a gigantic black changeling enchantress standing before you, connected to a strange machine with hollow green tubes. She looks concerned and angry. She is now limited in movement, but still extremely dangerous at close range");

	addLang('moon.event.s.0'  , "You manage to kill the giant enchantress. Moving past her body, you deactivate the machine.");
	addLang('moon.event.s.1'  , "You manage to kill the giant enchantress. Yet this victory is bitter-sweet, as Princess Selena is already dead.");
	addLang('moon.event.s.2'  , "The machine is deactivated");

	addLang('moon.event.t.0'  , "You break the glass.");

