	addLang('moon.event.o.1'  , "You slide down the dog tunnel.");

	addLang('moon.signV'      , '"Headquarters of her majesty Queen of the Moon."');
	addLang('moon.event.v.0'  , "The Queen of changelings, towers above you and laughs. <br /> 'You came far, but you see, since I have already taken Selena's power, no mortal in the universe can hope to defeat me. <br />Must be a shame for you having come so far and die so foolishly, huh?. But... Today I've decided to show mercy. I will give you an opportunity to return home alive, bearing my terms and conditions for a peaceful resolution. No, you can't have Selena's body. If you accept, just step through the portal besides me.'");

	addLang('moon.event.z.0'  , "A portal leading back home.");

