	addLang('moon.passageWrong'  , "You boldly enter the dark tunnel... <br />After a few steps, something pushes you from your feet and you slide down on slime-covered chute right into a cocoon full of yellow liquid.<br />You don't die immediately. Instead, you are used as an emotional food and a breeding host for changelings until your body gives up and then you are fed to the hive queen. Sucks to be you, but hey, you had it all before you died.");
	addLang('moon.passageRight'  , "You boldly enter the dark tunnel... <br />Carefully watching your step, you navigate through the slime-covered passages until you reach the hive.");

	addLang('ending.header.'+ FIELD_MOON +'.0' , "You were defeated.<br/>");
