	addLang('ending.header.'+ FIELD_MOON +'.2' , "Terrified, you accept Her Majesty's Menace's proposal and step into the portal home bearing scrolls with her demands.<br/>");
	addLang('ending.text.'+ FIELD_MOON +'.0', "In the following years, Queen Menace has repelled every assault on her fortress and grew in power until she became the true Goddess of Nightmares. Nopony could ever sleep safe since. Actually, this was true until Pinkie invented a time machine and everything sort of didn't happen, but this is another story.");
	addLang('ending.text.'+ FIELD_MOON +'.1', "Menace falls down. Green and yellow rays of power begin to shoot out of the holes of her deformed body. She screams in disbelief as her own power burns her to ash - Hh...how this is even possible??? I am a GODDESS!!! NOOOO!!!. You take Selena's body and step into the portal home, feeling sad, yet accomplished. At least, ponies can see good dreams again. Congratulations.");
	addLang('ending.text.'+ FIELD_MOON +'.1save', "Menace falls down. Green and yellow rays of power begin to shoot out of the holes of her deformed body. She screams in disbelief as her own power burns her to ash - Hh...how this is even possible??? I am a GODDESS!!! NOOOO!!!. You take Selena's body and step into the portal home, feeling sad, yet accomplished. At least, ponies can see good dreams again. Congratulations.");
	addLang('ending.text.'+ FIELD_MOON +'.1great', "Menace falls down. Green and yellow rays of power begin to shoot out of the holes of her deformed body. She screams in disbelief as her own power burns her to ash - Hh...how this is even possible??? I am a GODDESS!!! NOOOO!!!. You come back for Princess Selena and together you take the portal home. A great celebration was held at the castle and there was much joy and laughter, but then Pinkie decided to bring cookies from the past to eat them again and... But this is another story. Congratulations.");	
	addLang('ending.text.'+ FIELD_MOON +'.2', "The demands were rejected. Yet, information you gathered proved critical in the following assault on the lunar fortress that ended with a stalemate, leading to the well-known lunar peace treaty that legitimized the changeling colony on the moon. In return, Menace began taking duties as the watcher of nightmares for the pony nation.");
